sition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center bg-dem-gray-100 p-4\"><img alt=\"Alex Padilla\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-28 w-28 rounded-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Falex-padilla%20.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Falex-padilla%20.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Falex-padilla%20.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue to-dem-blue-light p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Alex Padilla</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/80\">U.S. Senator</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm text-dem-gray-600\">Alex Padilla represents California in the United States Senate. He was appointed in 2021 and subsequently elected in 2022 to a full term.\r\n</p><a href=\"https://www.padilla.senate.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\">Official Website<svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center bg-dem-gray-100 p-4\"><img alt=\"Adam Schiff\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-28 w-28 rounded-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Fadam-schiff%20.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Fadam-schiff%20.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Fadam-schiff%20.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue to-dem-blue-light p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Adam Schiff</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/80\">U.S. Senator</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm text-dem-gray-600\">Adam Schiff was elected to the U.S. Senate in 2024. He previously served as a U.S. Representative and chaired the House Intelligence Committee.\r\n</p><a href=\"https://www.schiff.senate.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\">Official Website<svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center bg-dem-gray-100 p-4\"><img alt=\"Jared Huffman\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-28 w-28 rounded-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Fjared-huffman%20.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Fjared-huffman%20.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fofficials%2Fjared-huffman%20.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue to-dem-blue-light p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-white\">Jared Huffman</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/80\">U.S. Representative, CA-02</p></div><div class=\"p-6\"><p class=\"text-sm text-dem-gray-600\">Congressman Jared Huffman represents California&#x27;s 2nd Congressional District, which includes Mendocino County. He is a champion for environmental protection, sustainable fisheries, and rural communities.\r\n</p><a href=\"https://huffman.house.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-semibold text-dem-blue hover:text-dem-blue-light\">Official Website<svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold text-dem-blue\"><span class=\"flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-dem-blue/10 text-lg\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-dem-blue\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z\"></path></svg></span>State Officials</h2><div class=\"grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-dem-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center bg-dem-gray-100 p-4\"><img alt=\"Gavin Newsom\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-28 w-28 rounded-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F